{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-461-almost-pi","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Uočenje 461: Ka Pi","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Acha <code>f(k, n)</code> = $e^\\frac{k}{n} - 1$, za sve neujemne celobrojke <code>k</code>.</p>\n<p>Iznenada, <code>f(6, 200) + f(75, 200) + f(89, 200) + f(226, 200)</code> = 3.1415926… ≈ π.</p>\n<p>Zapravo, je najbolja procena π od tipa <code>f(a, 200) + f(b, 200) + f(c, 200) + f(d, 200)</code>.</p>\n<p>Izraz <code>almostPi(n)</code> = a<sup>2</sup> + b<sup>2</sup> + c<sup>2</sup> + d<sup>2</sup> za a, b, c, d koji minimizuju greške: $\\lvert f(a,n) + f(b,n) + f(c,n) + f(d,n) - \\Pi\\rvert$</p>\n<p>Umepatiwa <code>almostPi(200)</code> = 6<sup>2</sup> + 75<sup>2</sup> + 89<sup>2</sup> + 226<sup>2</sup> = 64658.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f53a1000cf542c51004c","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302136,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-461-almost-pi"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function almostPi(n) {\n  \n  return true;\n}","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>almostPi</code> Trebalo bi da bude funkcija.</p>","testString":"assert.isFunction(almostPi);"},{"text":"<p><code>almostPi</code> Trebalo bi da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(typeof almostPi(10), 'number');"},{"text":"<p><code>almostPi(29)</code> mora vratiti <code>1208</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(almostPi(29), 1208);"},{"text":"<p><code>almostPi(50)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>4152</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(almostPi(50), 4152);"},{"text":"<p><code>almostPi(200)</code> treba da vrati <code>64658</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(almostPi(200), 64658);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-401-to-480","dashedName":"problem-461-almost-pi","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-462-permutation-of-3-smooth-numbers","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-460-an-ant-on-the-move","id":"5900f53a1000cf542c51004c","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-461-almost-pi"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}